{"tid":797714,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蔡瀾又改口話唔係所有日本人唔食得，好嘅日本人食得","createTime":"2018-08-28T17:04:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-29T09:15:35.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"9e6a80eae85f5c6249afa317ea88ceb9eb5f55ba","tid":797714,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T17:04:52.000Z","msg":"【三文魚真係有蟲？】蔡瀾現身說法 專家破解四大迷思 虹鱒算唔算係三文魚？（完整版）<br />\n2018-08-28  Bookmark<br />\n分享    <br />\n<br />\n近日內地《青海日報》報道，有業內團體把虹鱒歸類為三文魚，令食客人心惶惶。傳聞三文魚體内有大量寄生蟲，有人形容吃三文魚如同吃屎，何況是屬於淡水魚的虹鱒？但這些傳言究竟是人云亦云還是真有其事？這次邀請了香港理工大學郭穎軒博士，和香港魚類學會會長莊棣華為我們逐一講解！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://etw.nextdigital.com.hk/article/3_58599174/%E5%86%B7%E7%9F%A5%E8%AD%98/-%E4%B8%89%E6%96%87%E9%AD%9A%E7%9C%9F%E4%BF%82%E6%9C%89%E8%9F%B2--%E8%94%A1%E7%80%BE%E7%8F%BE%E8%BA%AB%E8%AA%AA%E6%B3%95-%E5%B0%88%E5%AE%B6%E7%A0%B4%E8%A7%A3%E5%9B%9B%E5%A4%A7%E8%BF%B7%E6%80%9D-%E8%99%B9%E9%B1%92%E7%AE%97%E5%94%94%E7%AE%97%E4%BF%82%E4%B8%89%E6%96%87%E9%AD%9A-\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fetw.nextdigital.com.hk%2Farticle%2F3_58599174%2F%25E5%2586%25B7%25E7%259F%25A5%25E8%25AD%2598%2F-%25E4%25B8%2589%25E6%2596%2587%25E9%25AD%259A%25E7%259C%259F%25E4%25BF%2582%25E6%259C%2589%25E8%259F%25B2--%25E8%2594%25A1%25E7%2580%25BE%25E7%258F%25BE%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E8%25AA%25AA%25E6%25B3%2595-%25E5%25B0%2588%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E7%25A0%25B4%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E5%259B%259B%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%25BF%25B7%25E6%2580%259D-%25E8%2599%25B9%25E9%25B1%2592%25E7%25AE%2597%25E5%2594%2594%25E7%25AE%2597%25E4%25BF%2582%25E4%25B8%2589%25E6%2596%2587%25E9%25AD%259A-&d=Vr7JYjVqTURLvFwOphuC9%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=52d76772\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://etw.nextdigital.com.hk/article/3_58599174/%E5%86%B7%E7%9F%A5%E8%AD%98/-%E4%B8%89%E6%96%87%E9%AD%9A%E7%9C%9F%E4%BF%82%E6%9C%89%E8%9F%B2--%E8%94%A1%E7%80%BE%E7%8F%BE%E8%BA%AB%E8%AA%AA%E6%B3%95-%E5%B0%88%E5%AE%B6%E7%A0%B4%E8%A7%A3%E5%9B%9B%E5%A4%A7%E8%BF%B7%E6%80%9D-%E8%99%B9%E9%B1%92%E7%AE%97%