gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又唔止肚餓又唔好食又高風險,係D白痴先咁鐘意爭住食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ad0807c1a7fae2755f8bebe074bb3ea9469ce1e","tid":797714,"uid":81783,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T05:36:17.000Z","msg":"蔡瀾老啦<br />\n<br />\n之前講三文魚比利益關係者屌到阿媽都唔認得<br />\n<br />\n而家老左梗係講圓滑d啦，咁老得罪人無還擊之力啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33588c8d02762c07337c9dedf0031105ad6da507","tid":797714,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T05:45:07.000Z","msg":"挪威三文魚係寒帶海域，一定安全過日本本土貨"},{"pid":"febe15e8012729322fd0424068fce522109e5f21","tid":797714,"uid":52595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T08:11:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5d005b0e1928da37589f32bc0eb676729d8638f8","tid":797714,"uid":126100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f48267d798c6a8722893b8b03f1a2c639811d25a","tid":797714,"uid":132038,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T05:19:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T08:14:22.000Z","msg":"三文魚唔食 AV 女優"}]}